name: AMBIDET速 F1-A
description: AMBIDET速 F1-A is a powdered, high performance, mildly chelated oil emulsifying soak cleaner. AMBIDET速 F1-A is uniquely formulated to allow for superior cleaning at low concentrations and temperatures, and can also be used remove stubborn oils and greases from brass and copper alloys. AMBIDET速 F1-A will provide excellent service life in extreme hard water applications.
